VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bWebViewController\b|\bWebViewWidget\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:scheme|canLaunchUrl|allowedSchemes|guard.*scheme|Uri\.parse.*scheme|navigationDelegate|onNavigationRequest
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Flutter WebView usage that may load user-controlled URLs without scheme or origin validation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for WebView Loading User-Controlled URL Without Scheme Validation.
